text: Ayumi Hamasaki's Arena Tour 2005 A: My Story was a nationwide tour of Japan that took place in early 2005 in order to promote her album, My Story and was released on DVD on August 24, 2005. Almost all the tracks on her My Story album were performed during the tour. ==Track listing== ===Disc 1 (Live)=== # Wonderland/Kaleidoscope (Opening) # Happy Ending # Inspire # Surreal # Unite! # Game # My Name's Women # About You # Moments # Walking Proud # Carols # Honey # Evolution # Boys & Girls ===Disc 2 (Encore)=== # Step You: MC # Humming 7/4 # Flower Garden # Replace # Special Screenies ===Disc 3 (Special Side)=== # Humming 7/4 MC # Off-stage shots collection # All Speeches (MC) collection Category:Ayumi Hamasaki video albums Category:2005 video albums Category:Live video albums Category:2005 live albums
title: Ayumi Hamasaki Arena Tour 2005 A
